{"tid":1779443,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[好文重溫]作為一個event organizer 見到你地依兩星期咁搞活動真係嘔撚晒血","createTime":"2019-12-11T16:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T16:51:50.000Z","uid":158504,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a489582482f17507446dad009948fe09609ca38","tid":1779443,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:11:23.000Z","msg":"發現最近大家又一次集體失憶<br />\n幫大家回憶下呢個討論咗68頁嘅post<br />\n<br />\n作為一個event organizer 見到你地依兩星期咁搞活動真係嘔撚晒血<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ajOggbU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ajOggbU</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. 一日十鳩幾個活動，就好似好撚豐富，但根本聚唔到人。<br />\n<br />\n2. 見撚到人哋宣傳緊啲活動，就咪撚同人哋撞時間； <br />\n<br />\n3. 成撚日諗住快閃，晏晝四點出post今晚18區開花，邊有可能宣傳得切。再加上好多人唔係全職抗爭，所以佢哋要時間去編排做自己私人嘅嘢，咁撚倉猝咪小人囉。<br />\n<br />\n4. 活動冇目的性，開花？即係做乜撚嘢呀？<br />\n<br />\n5. 宣傳時間太短，連登唔係主流平台，文宣一定要靠Facebook IG連儂牆AirDrop發放出去，所以最少要有三日去做宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n7. 我幾肯定，而家係有人鳩搞活動，目的打散人數。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再係咁樣鳩搞，只會狼來了，越嚟越冇人去啲活動。</span><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"63d7b73c8d6bfd58934d6734c5d5f0b833b966d2","tid":1779443,"uid":71494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d588a8c82c52d6d64f44b8979056bbf2e174aa81","tid":1779443,"uid":114792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:30:43.000Z","msg":"集會太多啦<br />\n搞唔掂"},{"pid":"e53556fce48c73c838fc8820b240079c3da436af","tid":1779443,"uid":149435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:33:56.000Z","msg":"再推！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f62e4798849db49c803ce73560088962ade5e2f","tid":1779443,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6506f71d65de2d6fe3051ca5315c3b93799e54c","tid":1779443,"uid":272371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:51:50.000Z","msg":"推"}]}